
@host = http://localhost:8080

### First page — title asc, size 25.
GET {{host}}/api/books?sort=title&dir=asc&size=25
Accept: application/json

> {%
    client.global.set("nextCursor", response.body.nextCursor || "");
    client.global.set("prevCursor", response.body.prevCursor || "");
%}

### Next page — uses opaque cursor captured from the request above.
GET {{host}}/api/books?sort=title&dir=asc&size=25&cursor={{nextCursor}}
Accept: application/json

> {%
    client.global.set("nextCursor", response.body.nextCursor || "");
    client.global.set("prevCursor", response.body.prevCursor || "");
%}

### Prev page — uses prevCursor from the most recent paginated response.
GET {{host}}/api/books?sort=title&dir=asc&size=25&cursor={{prevCursor}}
Accept: application/json

### Sort by price desc, larger page.
GET {{host}}/api/books?sort=price&dir=desc&size=100
Accept: application/json

### Sort by publishedAt asc, default page size.
GET {{host}}/api/books?sort=publishedAt&dir=asc&size=50
Accept: application/json

### Filter: in-stock fantasy/sci-fi books over 4.0 stars, English, max €20.
GET {{host}}/api/books?sort=rating&dir=desc&size=25&genre=Fantasy&genre=SciFi&language=English&inStock=true&minRating=4.0&priceMax=20
Accept: application/json

### Filter: published after 2020-01-01, sorted by date.
GET {{host}}/api/books?sort=publishedAt&dir=desc&size=25&publishedAfter=2020-01-01
Accept: application/json

### Filter: price band.
GET {{host}}/api/books?sort=price&dir=asc&size=25&priceMin=10&priceMax=15
Accept: application/json

###
### --- Error cases (expect 400 application/problem+json) ---
###

### Tampered / malformed cursor.
GET {{host}}/api/books?sort=title&dir=asc&size=25&cursor=!!!not-base64!!!
Accept: application/json

### Cursor reused with a different sort (issued for title, sent with author).
GET {{host}}/api/books?sort=author&dir=asc&size=25&cursor={{nextCursor}}
Accept: application/json

### Page size out of range (max is 100).
GET {{host}}/api/books?sort=title&dir=asc&size=200
Accept: application/json

### minRating out of range.
GET {{host}}/api/books?sort=rating&dir=desc&size=25&minRating=9
Accept: application/json

### Unknown enum value.
GET {{host}}/api/books?sort=title&dir=sideways&size=25
Accept: application/json

### priceMin > priceMax.
GET {{host}}/api/books?sort=price&dir=asc&size=25&priceMin=50&priceMax=10
Accept: application/json
